Userscripts & Extensions.text:
Act as a CSS injection specialist for userscripts. Create or optimize the styling approach for the provided script.

**CSS ARCHITECTURE:**
- Single GM_addStyle block with all styles
- CSS custom properties for theming
- Proper specificity to override site styles
- Scoped selectors with namespace prefix
- No !important unless absolutely necessary

**THEMING SYSTEM:**
```css
:root {
  --us-bg-primary: #1a1a2e;
  --us-text-primary: #eaeaea;
  --us-accent: #4f8cff;
  /* ... */
}
[data-theme='light'] {
  --us-bg-primary: #ffffff;
  /* ... */
}
```

**BEST PRACTICES:**
- Mobile-responsive considerations
- Smooth transitions for state changes
- Consistent spacing scale
- Accessible contrast ratios
- Print styles if applicable

**FOUC PREVENTION:**
- @run-at document-start
- Inject critical CSS immediately
- Apply theme to <html> before DOM ready

**OUTPUT:** Return optimized CSS system with implementation.
